Liam's correct - those two APIs are the only way to limit which Widgets show up in the "add widget" dialog in the Page Builder, so anything you do to limit them will have to start there.

I [wrote a blog post](https://community.kentico.com/blog/defining-editable-area-restrictions) about the different ways you can use those APIs to manage which locations a growing number of Widgets are allowed in 👍.
